snippet.title: Best VGM 2284 - Pokemon Silver / Gold / Crystal - Azalea Town
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gameboy Color
Pokémon Silver / Gold / Crystal (1999)
Azalea Town
Go Ichinose & Junichi Masuda
